headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Cummins (CMI) After A 62% One-Year Share Price Jump
summary: If you are wondering whether Cummins at around US$582 per share still offers value, you are not alone. This article is designed to walk you through what that price might really mean. The stock has returned 3.0% over the last 7 days, 12.1% over the past 30 days, 11.5% year to date, 62.2% over 1 year and 174.9% over 5 years, so many investors are asking whether the current level reflects opportunity or higher risk.
